Package com.phasmidsoftware.dsaipg.sort.elementary

package com.phasmidsoftware.dsaipg.sort.elementary
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    BubbleSort<X extends Comparable<X>>
    A class that implements the Bubble Sort algorithm for elements that implement the Comparable interface.
    HeapSort<X extends Comparable<X>>
    Implementation of the Heap Sort algorithm for sorting an array of elements that implement the Comparable interface.
    InsertionSort<X extends Comparable<X>>
    The InsertionSort class implements the insertion sort algorithm for sorting an array of elements that implement the Comparable interface.
    InsertionSortBasic<S>
    A generic implementation of the insertion sort algorithm.
    InsertionSortComparator<X>
    A class for performing insertion sort using a comparator, extending functionality from SortWithHelper.
    InsertionSortMSD
    This is a basic implementation of insertion sort for MSD Radix Sort.
    InsertionSortOpt<X extends Comparable<X>>
    Class InsertionSortOpt is an optimized version of InsertionSort.
    RandomSort<X extends Comparable<X>>
    Class to implement Random Sort.
    SelectionSort<X extends Comparable<X>>
    A class that implements the Selection Sort algorithm for arrays of elements that implement the Comparable interface.
    ShellSort<X extends Comparable<X>>
    Implementation of ShellSort, a generalization of insertion sort which allows the exchange of items that are far apart, defined by "gap" sequences.
    Solution
    The Solution class provides a static method for performing a binary search on a sorted array.
